| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2562 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d1bfc70e-b12f-5810-a80d-57bf563b3d7a"
